<h4>1. What data we collect</h4>
<p>
    RoomBooker collects only the information necessary to manage hotel room reservations:
</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Customer data:</strong> full name, email address, phone number.</li>
    <li><strong>Booking data:</strong> check-in and check-out dates, assigned room.</li>
</ul>

<h4>2. How we use your data</h4>
<p>
    The data collected is used exclusively for the purpose of managing reservations within this application.
    It is not shared with third parties, sold, or used for marketing purposes.
</p>

<h4>3. Data storage</h4>
<p>
    All data is stored in a secured PostgreSQL database hosted locally or on a private server.
    Access to the database is restricted and protected by credentials.
</p>

<h4>4. Your rights</h4>
<p>
    You have the right to request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal data
    stored in this system. To do so, please contact the system administrator.
</p>

<h4>5. Contact</h4>
<p>
    If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please reach out via the contact information
    provided by the administrator of this application.
</p>